<!-- TIPS -->
<div class="sg-section">
  <div class="sg-section-eyebrow">Make it stick</div>
  <div class="sg-section-title">6 Tips for Goals That Work</div>
  <div class="sg-tips-grid">
    <div class="sg-tip-card">
      <div class="sg-tip-num">TIP 01</div>
      <span class="sg-tip-icon">🎯</span>
      <div class="sg-tip-title">Write it down — physically</div>
      <div class="sg-tip-body">A goal in your head is just a thought. Write it down and you make a commitment. Keep it somewhere visible — your planner, your phone wallpaper, a sticky note on your mirror.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="sg-tip-card">
      <div class="sg-tip-num">TIP 02</div>
      <span class="sg-tip-icon">📊</span>
      <div class="sg-tip-title">Track progress, not just results</div>
      <div class="sg-tip-body">Celebrate the process. If your goal is to save $200, track every time you put $25 away. Each check-in keeps you motivated and shows how far you've come.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="sg-tip-card">
      <div class="sg-tip-num">TIP 03</div>
      <span class="sg-tip-icon">🔗</span>
      <div class="sg-tip-title">Connect goals to your bigger vision</div>
      <div class="sg-tip-body">Why does this goal matter? Link short-term goals to your long-term vision. "Complete my coding assignment" connects to "build a career in tech." The bigger picture makes hard days easier.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="sg-tip-card">
      <div class="sg-tip-num">TIP 04</div>
      <span class="sg-tip-icon">🤝</span>
      <div class="sg-tip-title">Tell someone — get accountability</div>
      <div class="sg-tip-body">Share your goal with your mentor or a brother in the program. Accountability is a superpower. Use HGP office hours for exactly this kind of follow-through.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="sg-tip-card">
      <div class="sg-tip-num">TIP 05</div>
      <span class="sg-tip-icon">🔁</span>
      <div class="sg-tip-title">Revise when life changes — don't quit</div>
      <div class="sg-tip-body">A goal that needs adjusting is not a failed goal. Change the deadline, adjust the amount, shift the approach. What kills a goal is abandoning it — not editing it.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="sg-tip-card">
      <div class="sg-tip-num">TIP 06</div>
      <span class="sg-tip-icon">📅</span>
      <div class="sg-tip-title">Schedule time to work on your goals</div>
      <div class="sg-tip-body">SMART goals tell you what to do. Time management tells you when. Block time for your goals just like HGP programming. If it's not scheduled, it doesn't happen.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

